'''''en-''''' is [[Quenya]] prefix equivalent to the English prefix "re-, again".<ref>{{PE|Eldarin}}, p.68</ref>

== Example ==
* '''enquanta-''' = "refill" ('''quanta-''' = "to fill")<ref>{{PE|Eldarin}}, p.167</ref>

== See also ==
* [[En-keladim]], a word with a similar prefix
